#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.tile.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.tile"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:1 of
msgid "Construct a tensor by repeating A the number of times given by reps."
msgstr "通过重复 A 给定次数来构造一个 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:3 of
msgid ""
"If `reps` has length ``d``, the result will have dimension of ``max(d, "
"A.ndim)``."
msgstr "如果 `reps` 的长度为 ``d``，则结果的维度将是 ``max(d, A.ndim)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:6 of
msgid ""
"If ``A.ndim < d``, `A` is promoted to be d-dimensional by prepending new "
"axes. So a shape (3,) array is promoted to (1, 3) for 2-D replication, or"
" shape (1, 1, 3) for 3-D replication. If this is not the desired "
"behavior, promote `A` to d-dimensions manually before calling this "
"function."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``A.ndim < d``，则通过在前面添加新轴将 `A` 提升为 d 维。例如，形状为"
" (3,) 的数组在 2D 复制时会变成 (1, 3)，在 3D 复制时变成 (1, 1, 3)。如果这"
"不是期望的行为，请在调用此函数之前手动将 `A` 提升为 d 维。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:12 of
msgid ""
"If ``A.ndim > d``, `reps` is promoted to `A`.ndim by prepending 1's to "
"it. Thus for an `A` of shape (2, 3, 4, 5), a `reps` of (2, 2) is treated "
"as (1, 1, 2, 2)."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``A.ndim > d``，则在 `reps` 前面添加 1 使其长度与 `A`.ndim 相同。"
"例如，对于形状为 (2, 3, 4, 5) 的 `A`，`reps` 为 (2, 2) 时会被视为 (1, 1, "
"2, 2)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:16 of
msgid ""
"Note : Although tile may be used for broadcasting, it is strongly "
"recommended to use MaxFrame's broadcasting operations and functions."
msgstr "注意：虽然 tile 可用于广播，但强烈建议使用 MaxFrame 的广播操作和函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:19 of
msgid "The input tensor."
msgstr "输入 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:21 of
msgid "The number of repetitions of `A` along each axis."
msgstr "`A` 沿每个轴重复的次数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:24 of
msgid "**c** -- The tiled output tensor."
msgstr "**c** -- 平铺后的输出 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`repeat`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:30 of
msgid "Repeat elements of a tensor."
msgstr "重复 tensor 中的元素。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`broadcast_to`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.tile.tile:33 of
msgid "Broadcast a tensor to a new shape"
msgstr "将 tensor 广播到新的形状"

